wiNltpS2R1LMyGiIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=c3a60264\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂]2019選民登記 推爆佢 7月2號截止<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1263306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1263306</a><br />\n[/麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]"}]}